ents immunizations are charged separately important information for your appointment schedule your appointment for a date at least six to eight weeks before departure bring your immunization record and or international certificate of vaccination the yellow card with you arrive at least 15 minutes before your appointment to complete our travel questionnaire international travel health history form pdf format or print it out from our site and bring the completed form with you up to one hour is scheduled for your appointment there is a no show charge for patients who cancel an appointment with less then 24 hours notice or who do not show up for their appointment back to top travel clinic staff margaret curry rn carolyn fox np dorothy marian rn nancy masunaga rn msn julie richards np sydney white rn back to top appointments 650 498 2336 extension 1 travel clinic hours related resources international travel health history form pdf vaden virtual health library first aid kit international travel more articles useful websites national center for infectious diseases of the centers for disease control shoreland's travel health on line division of vice provost for student affairs copyright board of trustees of leland stanford junior university site by wired moon
